<subSubSection pageNumber="801" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="801">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="801">
Note: 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Rubus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="fruticosus">Rubus fruticosus</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
, with the type designated by Weber, was proposed as conserved type of the genus by Jarvis (in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="801">Taxon</emphasis>
41: 573. 1992). This was eventually approved by the General Committee (see review of the history of this proposal by Barrie, 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="801">l.c.</emphasis>
55: 795-796. 2006).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
